Diversity in Child Mortality and Life Expectancy at Birth Among Major Tribes in 
Selected States of India.

Verma A(1), Sharma RK(2), Saha KB(3).

Author information:
(1)Indian Council of Medical Research (ICMR) - National Institute of Research in 
Tribal Health, Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India. Correspondence to: Dr Arvind 
