Cancer in Moroccan elderly: the first multicenter transverse study exploring the 
sociodemographic characteristics, clinical profile and quality of life of 
elderly Moroccan cancer patients.

Amzerin M(1)(2), Layachi M(3), Bazine A(4), Aassab R(5), Arifi S(6), Benbrahim 
Z(6), Khmamouche MR(7), Kairouani M(8), Raiss H(9), Majid N(10), Ouaouch S(11), 
