Author information:
(1)Ahmad Bin Zayed Al Nahyan Center of Cancer Treatment, Department of Medical 
Oncology, Tangier, Morocco. mounia.amzerin@gmail.com.
(2)Mohamed V University in Rabat, Faculty of Medicine and Pharmacy of Rabat, 
Rabat, Morocco. mounia.amzerin@gmail.com.
(3)Mohamed VI University Hospital, Department of Medical Oncology, Marrakech, 
Morocco.
(4)Moulay Ismail Military hospital, Department of Medical Oncology, Meknes, 
Morocco.
(5)Hassan II Hospital, Department of Medical Oncology, Agadir, Morocco.
