Epidemiology of Gastric Cancer in North Africa and the Middle East from 1990 to 
2017.

Ramazani Y(1), Mardani E(1), Najafi F(2), Moradinazar M(2), Amini M(3).

Author information:
(1)Behavioral Disease Research Center, Kermanshah University of Medical 
